This paper deals with the problem of physical layer multicasting (PLM) in massive MIMO systems, which involves designing efficient precoders and power control policies. This topic is closely related to several sub-fields of computer science, including information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), signal processing (cs.SI), multimedia (cs.MM), and game theory (cs.GT). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
